ai-kv16.8:1.3_0: They associate with pleasant feeling, painful, and neutral feeling.
ai-kv16.8:1.4_0: Then there is equanimity associated with the mind as object, there is also functionality. It is pervaded by the mind,
ai-kv16.8:1.5_0: And you don’t keep on doing it.
ai-kv16.8:1.7_0: Then there is no place for him, no footing for him, no footing in him,
ai-kv16.8:1.10_0: Without taking leave of him, there is no cycle of him, you should say,
ai-kv16.8:2.2_0: His objects there are generals, cycle, waists, and mobilizes.
ai-kv16.8:2.4_0: They truly understand form ... feeling ... perception ... choices ... consciousness.
ai-kv16.8:2.5_0: His objects there are gladnesses, cycles, and festering and troughly.
ai-kv16.8:2.6_0: And you don’t keep on doing it.
ai-kv16.8:3.2_0: Then there is no place for him, no footing for him, no footing in him,
ai-kv16.8:3.5_0: An object of his contemplation does not have rectitude. ...
ai-kv16.8:3.6_0: And you don’t keep on doing it.
ai-kv16.8:4.4_0: mental deeds that have been done by you,
ai-kv16.8:4.6_0: The results of deeds done away with one’s own mind,
ai-kv16.8:4.7_0: “Form has been done, the result of that form has arisen.”
